<P>To the Mo&s;t Wor&s;hipful GEORGE WASHINGTON PRESIDENT OF The UNITED STATES of AMERICA, The following DISCOURSE Is re&s;pectfully INSCRIBED, by his affectionate Brother and mo&s;t devoted Servant SAMUEL SEABURY.</P>
